sentence: Can you suggest some software courses that are easier than EECS 281 ?
sentence-with-vars: Can you suggest some software courses that are easier than department0 number0 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID WHERE LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%software%" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD < ( SELECT PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias1 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias1 ON PROGRAM_COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias1.COURSE_ID WHERE COURSEalias1.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias1.NUMBER = 281 ) ;
